OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with a little light rain at
OL,7,Ftimes. Some patches of haar possible
OL,8,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain or
OL,9,Fdrizzle. Fresh southeasterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FRain will clear Orkney in the
OL,12,Fmorning, then Shetland in the
OL,13,Fafternoon. Dry and bright for a few
OL,14,Fhours before showery rain spreads
OL,15,Fnorth in the afternoon. Occasionally
OL,16,Ffresh winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
